---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import ProximityHeading from '../../components/ProximityHeading'
import { projects } from '../../data/content'
---
<BaseLayout title="作品｜个人星球"><section class="section standalone-page"><div class="section-heading"><div><p class="eyebrow">SELECTED WORK</p><h2><ProximityHeading client:load label="正在生长的作品" /></h2></div><a class="text-button" href="/contact">一起合作 ↗</a></div><div class="project-grid">{projects.map((project, index) => <a class={`project-card project-${index + 1} reveal-link`} href={`/projects/${project.slug}`}><p>{project.type}</p><h3>{project.title}</h3><p>{project.desc}</p><span>{project.stack}</span></a>)}</div><div class="detail-block"><p class="eyebrow">HOW I BUILD</p><div class="process-grid"><article><span>01</span><h3>发现问题</h3><p>从真实使用场景开始，而不是从功能列表开始。</p></article><article><span>02</span><h3>设计路径</h3><p>将内容、交互和视觉组织为连贯体验。</p></article><article><span>03</span><h3>快速迭代</h3><p>通过可运行的原型不断验证与完善。</p></article></div></div></section></BaseLayout>
